{"tid":1599450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612六位義士，庭後問檢控及被告後有感","createTime":"2019-09-28T03:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T03:49:09.000Z","uid":61886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"90c40ad2aed5ccc370df1b9164f6f65728fdce2b","tid":1599450,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"//612 這六位義士。庭後問檢控及被告後有感：<br />\n<br />\n1. 他們搬鐵馬，犧牲了自己，我們才能佔領。<br />\n2. 全部拉低過口罩。<br />\n3. 影片有Open source plus police ，天眼。<br />\n4. 全部不是當場拉。<br />\n5. 上了小巴，沿途沒有口罩，天眼影到。<br />\n6. 所有八達通紀錄及銀行櫃員機紀錄，顯示行蹤。//<br />\n<br />\nFrom本土新聞 Local Press Fb<br />\n<br />\n手足請做好保護<br />\n一離開屋企就要小心<br />\n唔好落左場就當無事<br />\n<br />\n港共政府會開始秋後算帳大搜捕"},{"pid":"31b9ff4b908ce3ecceacc3bd4f2d1fc14f175684","tid":1599450,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07R3qL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07R3qL1.jpg&h=8de0bfc3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}